File Transfer Tool for NGS portal installation guide
====================================================

REQUIRED TOOLS (OUR WORKING VERSION)
------------------------------------
 o J2SE SDK with JNDI (v1.4.2_05), http://java.sun.com/j2se
 o Jakarta Ant (1.6.2), http://ant.apache.org/
 o Java CoG (1.1), http://www-unix.globus.org/cog/java/
 o Jakarta Tomcat (5.0.27), http://jakarta.apache.org/tomcat
 o CHEF (1.2.10), http://collab.sakaiproject.org/portal
 o CHEF GridService module (org.chefproject.service.GridService)

INSTALL
-------
 o Set parameters in "build.properties"
   "chef-portal.home" -- where CHEF is deployed
   "chef-src.home" -- where CHEF source exists with the library in dist/lib
   "jars" -- all libary files needed including Java CoG library
   "module-mgrid" -- where module GridService libary exists
 o Execute "ant build" to build
 o Shutdown Tomcat if it is running
 o Execute "ant build" to build
 o Execute "ant deploy" to deploy, you also need all libraries defined by
   "chef-portal.home", "chef-src.home", "jars" and "module-mgrid" copied to CHEF
 o Add it as a tool in your CHEF
 o You may need to set ~/.globus/cog.proterties on your web server for whom
   Tomcat is running if you have firewall protecting your web server
        cacert=/etc/grid-security/certificates/01621954.0
        tcp.port.range=65000,65255
        ip=your_web_server_ip_address
 o Restart Tomcat


